data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! 1 acre cul-de-sac lot in Springtown ISD! No city taxes. This beautiful home has it all. Stately knotty pine cabinets with lots of granite countertop in this well appointed kitchen. The dining room overlooks the peaceful backyard. The 4th room would make a beautiful home office, playroom, or guest room. This backyard offers a surprise at every turn. A huge covered back porch with a wood burning fireplace. Extended covered patio with hot tub. And a chicken coop! You won't want to miss the epic 40x40 workshop! It has endless possibilities with a bathroom, 220 and 110 amp wiring, 2 oversized roll top bay doors for boats, RV's and big trucks. Parking is a breeze here with the 3 car garage at the main home and a covered carport behind the gate. Come enjoy the country life with quick access to major thoroughfares.
